name: BTV Frequencies 004 - The FU Hand
description: Beyond the Void series by RocketSpaceboy. The BTV Frequencies work examines the frequencies received in the interdimensional existence beyond space and time. This specific piece is part of the Frequencies Collection.  Locked in the frequencies cast out beyond the void is a realm of 2 dimension horror. This particular image displaying the FU Hand gives us a look at the more tame side of this realm where cartoon murder and fright is a common place.
